{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudscheckboxitemindeterminate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some checkboxes components."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If you want to use a checkbox with only an indicator prefer instead "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"platforms":[{"unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"macOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","deprecated":false},{"name":"tvOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"16.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false},{"unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"1.0","deprecated":false},{"name":"watchOS","beta":false,"introducedAt":"11.0","deprecated":false,"unavailable":false}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents29OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminateV","symbolKind":"struct","title":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Structure"},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/init(selection:label:description:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:constrainedMaxWidth:action:)"],"anchor":"Initializers","generated":true},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/body"],"anchor":"Instance-Properties","generated":true},{"title":"Default Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate\/View-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations","generated":true}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Layouts","level":2,"anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing checkbox indicator and a leading optional image"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Indicator states","level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The checkbox indicator has three available states:"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is filled with a tick, the user has made the action to select the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"unselected"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": the checkbox is empty, does not contain a tick, the user has made the action to unselect or did not select yet the checkbox","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"indeterminate","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": mike a prefilled or preticked checkbox, the user did not do anything on it yet"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If you need a checkbox with only two states to manage use instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Particular cases","level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In addition, the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but this component must not be considered as disabled."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component does not follow the right-to-left (RTL) \/ left-to-right (LTR) mode returned by the system as it could have some meaning"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to have for example the indicator in trailing position for LTR mode and vice versa."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However, if the component has an icon in leading position (RTL mode) or in trailing position (LTR), the content of the icon is never changed."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It could lead to a loss of meaning or semantics in the icon. Thus a specific flag can be used to flip the icon content whatever the layout direction is."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It prevents the user do implement its own rules to flip or not image."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Accessibility considerations","level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom checkbox trait."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Forbidden by design","level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an indeterminate state checkbox","    @Published var selection: OUDSCheckboxIndicatorState = .indeterminate","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and a description as helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Bazinga!\", description: \"Doll-Dagga Buzz-Buzz Ziggety-Zag\")","","    \/\/ A trailing checkbox with a label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The reversed layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  description: \"Of dreaming boys and wide-eyed girls\",","                                  isReversed: true,","                                  icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection,","                                  label: \"We live in a fabled world\",","                                  isError: true,","                                  errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                                  hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\")","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ A leading checkbox with a label and and icon but with the icon flipped vertically","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  label: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related checkbox as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(selection: $selection, label: \"Hello world\", isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you want to manage the RTL mode quite easily and switch your layouts (flip image, indicator in RTL leading i.e. in the right):"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    @Environment(\\.layoutDirection) var layoutDirection","","    OUDSCheckboxItemIndeterminate(isOn: $selection,","                                  label: \"Cocorico !\",","                                  icon: Image(systemName: \"figure.handball\"),","                                  flipIcon: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft,","                                  isInversed: layoutDirection == .rightToLeft)"],"type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Suggestions","level":2,"anchor":"Suggestions","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"According to the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the checkbox by default must be used in unselected state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Design documentation","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-checkbox","isActive":true,"overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"text":"unified-design-system.orange.com","type":"text"}],"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"unified-design-system.orange.com"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading"},{"text":"Orange","level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Orange Business Tools","level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_OrangeBusinessTools","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Sosh","level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"2.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Version","type":"aside"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside"}]}],"references":{"component_checkboxItem_Orange":{"identifier":"component_checkboxItem_Orange","alt":"A checkbox it